STEAMGAMERS.COM | MiniGames | *Funtastic* @ 72.26.196.164:27015
The T's fly out of the boost holes with a hegrenade and have to try and pick off the CT's who are behind the wall by throwing the grenades at them. The CT's have to shoot down the T's in mid air. There is a HE vending machine in T spawn to make it easier for the T's to pick up grenades and go again. There are 10 CT slots and 16 T slots to allow to try and balance the teams, this map was designed for a 20 slot server. Big thanks to [RuMe] Impossible for retexturing my map! Check us out at www.steamgamers.com The map is running on the following servers: MiniGames Funtastic {66.135.43.185:27016} Final Version: I remade the map from start, its pretty much similar but looks alot nicer on the eye. Final_Improved: The map was retextured thanks to [RuMe] Impossible! Big thank you to him! Thanks!
